{"tid":508554,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"老婆係Jessica. C係咪真係想日日做？","createTime":"2017-12-24T11:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T03:02:01.000Z","uid":48350,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bb02809a8e0ee7edd0bc57b7ea1d319f9c30c160","tid":508554,"uid":48350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/191326_caeb133ea39eed03cfc024db5b3daae6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F191326_caeb133ea39eed03cfc024db5b3daae6.jpeg&h=77c5da6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n名模Jessica C.（JC）於社交平台宣布懷有第二胎，她於聖誕樹前拍片，先表示老公安志杰（Andy）送了耳環給她作聖誕節禮物，隨後就表示懷孕，用手掂住肚仔，仲加咗紅色禮物絲帶，示意bb係一份聖誕禮物，她寫道：「Very grateful for my Christmas gifts!P.s not from Santa。（好感激呢份聖誕禮物！）」她更hashtag了第兩個bb，拍攝時全程笑晒口，難掩喜悅，更獲不少網民恭喜。 <br />\n<br />\nJC與影星安志杰（Andy）於2015年馬爾代夫訂婚，去年三月未婚誕下囡囡Tessa，今年十月於夏威夷舉行婚禮，囡囡更做花女。JC一直都恨有第二胎，早排JC與Andy出席活動時已講要日日做，仲話想造聖誕bb，原來當時已經懷孕。現時懷孕三個多月的JC，跟足傳統三個月先宣布喜訊，怕bb小器，JC向東網表示：「我好開心同好興奮，未知性別！」JC仲揀平安夜宣布，Tessa要當家姐了！ <br />\n<br />\nJC接受訪問時表示：「我好開心同好興奮，未知BB性別，今次係預期之內，初期冇胃口，之前個肚都係扁，今胎特別攰，12月嗰肚先脹脹哋，依家15周。」而經理人表示：「因為第一胎雙方家長都想見證，所以大女Tessa喺美國出世，今胎就要就Andy工作檔期，有機會喺香港出世。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171224/mobile/bkn-20171224164529648-1224_00862_001.html?eventid=402883474d7616cc014d99b7ab6e49b4&amp;eventsection=hk_entertainment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171224%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171224164529648-1224_00862_001.html%3Feventid%3D402883474d7616cc014d99b7ab6e49b4%26eventsection%3Dhk_entertainment&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f124b417\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171224/mobile/bkn-20171224164529648-1224_00862_001.html?eventid=402883474d7616cc014d99b7ab6e49b4&amp;eventsection=hk_entertainment</a>"},{"pid":"4faecf7794d0ed06da927e20272d96314817f973","tid":508554,"uid":103684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89ce236dfa711b482f347611d12ab257b70da9a","tid":508554,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"假波"},{"pid":"bc50e39a9f3bd8f783b08ecfe4d186b0503c74ff","tid":508554,"uid":48350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89ce236dfa711b482f347611d12ab257b70da9a","tid":508554,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"假波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"唔係拆左彈喇咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926914c5518c4a10238dc59a868059ce1c646da8","tid":508554,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"哇！"},{"pid":"af24eaa877350e439701c6f9dc3d88cbf892ec7b","tid":508554,"uid":154186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"日日都要防偷錢"},{"pid":"f3f1311a0c61f259fd82280fe046dca5e5fc70d3","tid":508554,"uid":146558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/191326_caeb133ea39eed03cfc024db5b3daae6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F191326_caeb133ea39eed03cfc024db5b3daae6.jpeg&h=77c5da6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmo